<% content_for :title, "Reports" %>

<div class="grid gap-5 lg:grid-cols-3">
  <div class="rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-card">
    <p class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-500">Ready Reports</p>
    <p class="mt-3 text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-900">0</p>
  </div>
  <div class="rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-card">
    <p class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-500">Pending Generation</p>
    <p class="mt-3 text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-900"><%= @review_cycles.count { |cycle| cycle.status == "closed" } %></p>
  </div>
  <div class="rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-card">
    <p class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-500">Delivered</p>
    <p class="mt-3 text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-900">0</p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-shell">
  <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-slate-400">Reports</p>
  <h3 class="mt-2 text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Cycle reports dashboard</h3>
  <p class="mt-3 max-w-2xl text-sm leading-6 text-slate-500">
    Completed cycles will appear here once report generation and delivery workflows are connected. Reports compare self-review scores against anonymised peer averages by key behaviour category and keep peer comments anonymous.
  </p>

  <div class="mt-8 grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2 xl:grid-cols-3">
    <div class="rounded-3xl border border-dashed border-slate-300 bg-slate-50 p-5">
      <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700">Key behaviours comparison</p>
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-500">Show peer feedback average scores beside self-review scores for the configured comparison categories.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="rounded-3xl border border-dashed border-slate-300 bg-slate-50 p-5">
      <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700">Anonymous peer comments</p>
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-500">Aggregate peer comments by category without exposing reviewer identity.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="rounded-3xl border border-dashed border-slate-300 bg-slate-50 p-5">
      <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700">Manager feedback summary</p>
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-500">Display manager score and narrative separately from the anonymised peer comparison table.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
